<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.3.11">
<l>tāḷpa rappimaṇ tāviya vīcaṉai</l>
<l>nīḷpo ḻilkuru kūrccaṭa kōpaṉcol</l>
<l>kēḻil lāyirat tippattum vallavar</l>
<l>vāḻvar vāḻveyti ñālam pukaḻavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master these ten in the matchless thousand</l> 
<l>spoken by Caṭakōpaṉ of Kuṟukūr with long groves</l>
<l>on the lord who spanned the earth, expanding [his] foot</l>
<l>will live, reaching life while the world praises.</l> 

      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
